OL,3,CElectric bus stolen and damaged days
OL,4,Cafter launch of free service
OL,6,FA free city centre bus was stolen and
OL,7,Fthen returned "significantly" damaged
OL,8,Fjust a week after the new service was
OL,9,Flaunched.
OL,11,FThe Sheffield Connect electric bus was
OL,12,Ffound outside the city centre in the
OL,13,Fearly hours of Monday 15 April.
OL,15,FSouth Pennine Buses, which operates
OL,16,Fthe shuttle service, confirmed two
OL,17,Fbuses had been broken into with "at
OL,18,Fleast one" stolen. Other buses and
OL,19,Fproperty were also targeted and
OL,20,Fvandalised in the incident.
