OL,6,FDebris from the bus was later found
OL,7,Fdiscarded following an apparent crash
OL,8,Fin the Killamarsh area.
OL,10,FThe new free bus service began on 8
OL,11,FApril with four vehicles serving the
OL,12,Fcity seven days a week.
OL,14,FRunning every seven to eight minutes,
OL,15,Fthe electric bus, aimed to reduce
OL,16,Fcarbon emissions in the city.
