OL,3,CElectric bus stolen and damaged days
OL,4,Cafter launch of free service
OL,6,FCllr Ben Miskell, chair of the
OL,7,Fcouncil's transport committee, said at
OL,8,Fthe time of the launch: "This is an
OL,9,Fimportant and exciting moment in the
OL,10,Fhistory of Sheffield, not only are we
OL,11,Fintroducing the city's first zero
OL,12,Femissions buses to our streets, but a
OL,13,Fservice that is completely free for
OL,14,Fpeople to use."
OL,16,FPolice have launched an investigation.
