OL,3,CElectric bus stolen and damaged days
OL,4,Cafter launch of free service
OL,6,FA South Yorkshire Police spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "It is reported that a Sheffield
OL,8,FConnect bus was taken during the night
OL,9,Ffrom the Sheffield Interchange, but
OL,10,Fthen later returned in the early hours
OL,11,Fof the morning.
OL,13,F"It is also reported that the bus has
OL,14,Fbeen significantly damaged."
OL,16,FSouth Pennine Buses director Kevin
OL,17,FCarr said that the incident had been
OL,18,F"very upsetting" but it was working
OL,19,F"incredibly hard" to minimise any
OL,20,Fdisruption.
